# .forge/state/

This directory holds FORGE instrumentation state. Files written here are
ephemeral runtime artifacts (active-tab markers, checkpoint files,
audit logs) — they are NOT spec evidence and most are gitignored
in consumer projects.

Canonical files (Spec 368):
- score-audit.jsonl — predicted/observed score calibration log.
  Schema versioned via the `schema_version` field in each record
  (currently `1`). Adjacent instrumentation streams (e.g. Spec 247
  operator-effort attribution) extend this schema under additive
  keys; they SHALL NOT introduce parallel `.jsonl` files.

See: docs/process-kit/score-calibration-loop.md.
